FAQ

- What is the new 5G Technology? [icon](https://te eg/wps/wcm/connect/3aacd409-4f55-4a45-91d2-8a90fcce9cbb/add-circle png? [icon](https://te eg/wps/wcm/connect/f5396289-88af-4b1f-8b10-ebc71734badc/minus-circle
documents.title: 5G

documents.text:
f5396289-88af-4b1f-8b10-ebc71734badc/minus-circle png? 

- 5G is the fifth generation of cellular technology, representing a significant advancement over previous generations It's designed to enhance speed, lower latency (delay), and provide greater flexibility for wireless services, enabling the transmission of larger volumes of data compared to older networks - Do I need to be in a 5G coverage area to use it? [icon](https://te eg/wps/wcm/connect/3aacd409-4f55-4a45-91d2-8a90fcce9cbb/add-circle png?
documents.title: 5G

documents.text:
cd409-4f55-4a45-91d2-8a90fcce9cbb/add-circle png? [icon](https://te eg/wps/wcm/connect/f5396289-88af-4b1f-8b10-ebc71734badc/minus-circle png? 

- Yes, to experience 5G speeds, you need to be in a location with WE’s 5G coverage The 5G network is expanding across Egypt to reach more areas - What do I need to use 5G Technology? [icon](https://te eg/wps/wcm/connect/3aacd409-4f55-4a45-91d2-8a90fcce9cbb/add-circle png? [icon](https://te eg/wps/wcm/connect/f5396289-88af-4b1f-8b10-ebc71734badc/minus-circle
documents.title: 5G

documents.text:
f5396289-88af-4b1f-8b10-ebc71734badc/minus-circle png? 

- You will need to be in an area covered by 5G network (as coverage will be available gradually) and you should also have 5G enabled mobile handset - Should I change my tariff or pay extra fees to use 5G services? [icon](https://te eg/wps/wcm/connect/3aacd409-4f55-4a45-91d2-8a90fcce9cbb/add-circle png? [icon](https://te eg/wps/wcm/connect/f5396289-88af-4b1f-8b10-ebc71734badc/minus-circle
documents.title: 5G

documents.text:
f5396289-88af-4b1f-8b10-ebc71734badc/minus-circle png? 

- No need as WE is providing the 5G benefits with no extra fees or subscription All what you will need is to enable 5G service on you device and to be in an area covered by 5G All existing tariffs will enjoy 5G service for free But we recommend upgrading your mobile internet bundle as using 5G high quality internet services takes higher mobile data consumption rates - What happens if I leave a 5G coverage area? [icon](https://te
documents.title: 5G

Quota & Flexibility

 

 

## Flexible Minutes & Mobile Internet Usage

With WE Gold, use your minutes and mobile internet allowance with more flexibility

- Local minutes to WE or other networks will be charged 1:1
- Mobile internet will be charged 1:1
- If you run out of mobile internet, you can get mobile gigabytes using your minutes bundle with a rate (1 mobile megabyte = 1 minute)
- If you run out of mobile internet and minutes, you can get mobile gigabytes using your fixed internet bundle with a rate (1 mobile megabyte = 20 fixed internet megabytes)
- No separate allowance for SMS, it will be deducted from local minutes allowance (1 SMS = 1 minute)
- Unused mobile internet gigabytes will be carried over to the following month
- If you consume all the minutes and mobile internet, you can follow any of the below options:
 - You will be charged for the mobile internet by any of the below options:
 - Subscribe in any of [Nitro add-ons](https://te
documents.title: WE Gold

documents.text:
- Subscribe in any of [Nitro add-ons](https://te eg/wps/portal/te/Personal/Mobile/Nitro-mobile-internet)
 - Or paying 5 EGP for every 200 MBs
 - You will be charged 14 Pts to 1 minute or 1 SMS ADSL Flexibility

Also with WE Gold, you can enjoy WE Air subscription

- You can enjoy only one of the two services, either fixed internet or WE Air, not both

- After consuming the main bundle, you can add extra add-ons with additional fees - WE Air bundle can’t be shared with family members

Travel Experience

 

 

## Unique Travel Experience With WE Gold:

Enjoy traveling abroad with WE Gold and get international minutes and data roaming all year round

## 1\
documents.title: WE Gold

al minutes and data roaming all year round

## 1\ International Minutes Bundle:

- Starting WE Gold 525, you will be granted monthly international minutes - International minutes are not carried over to the next month - Upon consuming your granted minutes, you will be charged with current international minute rates - International minutes are available exclusively to WE Gold customers - Current roaming receiving minutes rates will apply
documents.title: WE Gold

documents.text:
urrent roaming receiving minutes rates will apply - The minutes are not eligible for usage in the "hard to reach" countries For more details visit [https://te eg/sl/InterRoaming](https://te eg/sl/InterRoaming)

## 2\ Data Roaming Bundle:

- WE Gold customers are eligible for two data roaming bundles twice a year, and every bundle is valid for one week from the time of activating the bundle - The data roaming quota differs according to each price point
documents.title: WE Gold

documents.text:
aming quota differs according to each price point - The maximum data roaming bundles are 2 bundles per year - You can add extra data roaming bundles with extra fees that will be added to your monthly bill - You can activate the data roaming bundle through My WE app, \*800# or by calling 500 - The MBs are not eligible for usage in the "hard to reach" countries For more details visit [https://te eg/sl/InterRoaming](https://te eg/sl/InterRoaming)

## 3\ WE Flight:

- Starting WE Gold 1300, enjoy outgoing calls to Egypt and the rest of the world by dialing \*800\*11# during your flight as per the below table:

| WE Gold | Number of outgoing minutes per year |
| -- | -- |
| WE Gold 1300 | 4 Minutes / twice a year |
| WE Gold 200 | 6 Minutes / 3 times a year |

- To know more about WE Flight service eligible airlines, please visit [https://te eg/sl/WEFlight](https://te eg/sl/WEFlight)

1 Switch your phone on, make sure airplane mode is off 2 Your phone will automatically connect to the AeroMobile network

- To migrate from other networks to WE Gold, you must visit the nearest WE branch and the migration process will be completed within only 24 hours
documents.title: WE Gold

documents.text:
on process will be completed within only 24 hours ## Enjoy Sharing Your Bundle With Your Family

- You can share your minutes and mobile gigabytes with up to 6 members according to each price point
- You can add extra members to family group with 10 EGP per member and the fees will to be added to your monthly bill
- Family members can be subscribers of any of the following plans (12Pts, Kix, Super Kix, New Kix, Kix Plus, Tazbeet, Indigo 5, 45, 105, 225, 375 or 750)
- You can add family members and share your bundle through My WE app,\*800# or call the call center on 500 for more details
documents.title: WE Gold

documents.text: # or call the call center on 500 for more details - Once the member is added to the family group, you should add consumption limit to the minutes and mobile gigabytes - Consumption limits are renewed automatically on monthly basis In case the family group owner adjusted the limit, the new limit will be renewed automatically - You can also pay the mobile payments of your family members either partially or fully - Family group owner can modify or delete the members
documents.title: WE Gold

mily group owner can modify or delete the members Members also can remove themselves from the group - Family group members can’t either join any other family groups nor he/she could be an owner of a another family group

- You will accumulate monthly points to be redeemable at WE stores and WE Bonus partners network
- Each WE Gold bundle will be granted monthly bonus points when paying the monthly invoice, excluding taxes and installments

- In case of bundle upgrading or downgrading during the year you will receive the voucher according to the bundle with the longer period
- You will be eligible to receive your first device voucher after paying 12 complete bills excluding prorated bills, after 12 months from joining WE Gold with condition that there are no due bills

## الشروط والاحكام:

- خدمة اظهار رقم الطالب تتيح للعميل معرفة رقم المتصل
documents.title: أنظمة التليفون المنزلي

documents.text:
دمة اظهار رقم الطالب تتيح للعميل معرفة رقم المتصل - خدمة التتبع تتيح للعميل تحويل مكالمات الخط الارضي الخاصة به الي خط ارضي اخر او موبايل WE - الدقائق غير المستخدمة لا يتم ترحيلها الي الفترة المحاسبية التالية - امكانية الاستعلام عن الفاتوره والباقات والخدمات الاضافيه عن طريق تطبيق [https://my te eg](https://my te eg/) My WE الخدمة الصوتية 11 - في حالة عدم سداد الفاتورة الشهرية سيتم تطبيق قواعد القطع والرفع  كما يلي :
 - يتم اصدار الفاتورة شهريا - فترة السماح لمدة 20 يوم من تاريخ اصدار الفاتورة
documents.title: أنظمة التليفون المنزلي

documents.text: - فترة السماح لمدة 20 يوم من تاريخ اصدار الفاتورة - تحويل الخط للاستقبال فقط في اليوم التالي من انتهاء فترة السماح ولمدة 7 ايام - ايقاف الخط يتم بعد انتهاء فترة الاستقبال
documents.title: أنظمة التليفون المنزلي

documents.text:
7 ايام - ايقاف الخط يتم بعد انتهاء فترة الاستقبال | | | | | -- | -- | -- | | **اصدار الفاتوره** | **الاستقبال فقط** | **الرفع المؤقت** | | الخدمه ستكون متاحه لاجراء واستقبال المكالمات لمدة 20 يوم من تاريخ اصدار الفاتوره | سيتم تحويل الخدمه للاستقبال فقط لمدة 7 ايام | سيتم رفع الخدمه مؤقتا مما يؤثر علي خدمة الانترنت المنزلي | | مثال :
اصدار الفاتوره في 1 يناير
فترة السماح: من 1 يناير وحتي 20 يناير | من 21 يناير وحتي 27 يناير | بدءا من 28 يناير سيتم رفع الخدمه مؤقتا مما يؤثر علي خدمة الانترنت المنزلي | - يمكن للعميل سداد الفاتوره المستحقة من خلال قنوات السداد التالية: - تطبيق My WE  باستخدام بطاقه بنكيه

 - جميع فروع WE
 - احد منافذ الدفع الالكتروني (فوري مصاري سداد بي ممكن خدماتي الخ )

documents.title: باقات X

ت علي يوتيوب و كمان مواقع اكتر للسوشيال و المزيكا | الباقة | السعر(جنيه) | الصلاحية |
| -- | -- | -- |
| **X** | 20 جنيه | 30 يوم |
| **X Plus** | 50 جنيه | 30 يوم |

**باقة X:**

- الباقة متاحة لجميع عملاء باقات كنترول – كنترول تظبيط \- اهلاوي او عملاء الفاتورة او خطوط الداتا الحاليين والجدد ولعملاء 12 قرش متاحة كباقة اضافية علي باقات الموبايل انترنت الاساسية (لسة الباقة شغالة)
documents.title: باقات X

documents.text:
باقات الموبايل انترنت الاساسية (لسة الباقة شغالة) يمكن الاشتراك من خلال #20\*990\* و لعملاء خط الداتا للاشتراك اطلب \*99#
- يمكن استخدام الباقة علي مواقع السوشيال المحددة (Facebook Browsing , WhatsApp, FB Messenger, Google Maps) - فيديوهات Facebook ليست من ضمن الباقة و سيتم محاسبتها من الباقة الاساسية
 - مكالمات WhatsApp من ضمن باقة X
- في حالة استخدام مواقع اخري (غير التي تم تحديدها) سيتم خصم الاستهلاك من الباقة الاساسية و بعد انتهاء الباقة الاساسية سيتم المحاسبة خارج الباقة علي حسب نظام الخط

## Flexible Minutes & Mobile Internet Usage

With WE Gold, use your minutes and mobile internet allowance with more flexibility

- Local minutes to WE or other networks will be charged 1:1
- Mobile internet will be charged 1:1
- If you run out of mobile internet, you can get mobile gigabytes using your minutes bundle with a rate (1 mobile megabyte = 1 minute)
- If you run out of mobile internet and minutes, you can get mobile gigabytes using your fixed internet bundle with a rate (1 mobile megabyte = 20 fixed internet megabytes)
- No separate allowance for SMS, it will be deducted from local minutes allowance (1 SMS = 1 minute)
- Unused mobile internet gigabytes will be carried over to the following month
- If you consume all the minutes and mobile internet, you can follow any of the below options:
 - You will be charged for the mobile internet by any of the below options:
 - Subscribe in any of [Nitro add-ons](https://te
